qtemp-Perl                                                    Version 0.01
==========================================================================

qtemp-Perl - qtemp templates for assintance writing Perl.

SYNOPSIS

qtemp perl -o new-script

qtemp perl-lib -o NewLibrary.pm

qtemp perl-sub -d name=new_sub -d instance

qtemp perl-exporter

INSTALLATION

Download the latest release ('qtemp-Perl-0.01.tar.gz'), navigate to the
download directory and install it with the command.
    tar xvzf qtemp-Perl-0.01.tar.gz -o ~/.qtemp/

TIPS

The perl-sub and perl-exporter templates are most useful in a text editor
like 'vim' which allows piping of shell commands. 'qtemp' can be piped in
to vim by pressing '!' when in visual select mode.

MORE INFO

For more information about qtemp, 
    see its github page (https://github.com/bmatsuo/qtemp)
